metadata.name: This is not the end
metadata.description:
Drawn for ukrainedao.eth

Ukraine and Uzbekistan, my homeland, are far apart, but I didn't perceive this country as something foreign. I have many friends and colleagues from there, my relatives live there.

And from the moment Russia started the war, I share all the pain and anxiety for Ukraine and its people who have to go through all this.

I believe that Ukraine will be able to cope with all the difficulties on its way, will preserve itself, and people will stop dying.

February 26, 2022
